<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.273010>
    dc:description "FIGURE 59. Geodia pocillum sp. nov., a, habitus of holotype RMNH Por. 10547 (scale bar = 1 cm), a 1, habitus of the two paratypes RMNH Por. 9796 (scale bar = 1 cm), a 2, concentrated uniporal oscules in the small globular paratype, b – k, SEM images of spicules, b, long thin oxea, b 1, detail of apex of b, c, fusiform oxea, c 1, detail of apex of c, d, orthotriaene, d 1, cladome of d, d 2, cladome of a smaller orthotriaene, e, anatriaene, e 1, cladome of anatriaene, f, protriaene, f 1, cladome of protriaene, g, small cortical oxea, h, sterraster, h, detail of surface of sterraster, i, large oxyaster, j, small oxyaster, k, strongylospheraster." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/273010/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

